<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>AI on ifindv's Blog</title><link>https://ifindv.github.io/tags/ai/</link><description>Recent content in AI on ifindv's Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>© 2026 ifindv</copyright><lastBuildDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ifindv.github.io/tags/ai/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Claude Code 教程系列：内存系统（Memory）</title><link>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/2026-04-23-claude-code-tutorial-02-memory/</link><pubDate>Thu, 23 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/2026-04-23-claude-code-tutorial-02-memory/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;内存系统使Claude能够在多个会话和对话中保持持久化的上下文。与临时上下文窗口不同，内存文件允许你在团队间共享项目标准、存储个人开发偏好、维护特定目录的规则，并将外部文档导入为版本控制的一部分。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Claude Code 教程系列：斜杠命令</title><link>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/2026-04-22-claude-code-tutorial-01-slash-commands/</link><pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ifindv.github.io/posts/2026-04-22-claude-code-tutorial-01-slash-commands/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;斜杠命令是Claude Code中最基础的快捷方式，通过 &lt;code&gt;/命令名&lt;/code&gt;的语法快速调用预定义功能。无论是内置命令还是自定义命令，都能让你在开发过程中更高效地与Claude交互。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>